dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, and spot heights, Lower right margin : "Ek tou lithographeiou tēs Geōgraphikēs Hypēresias Stratou" Date in lower left margin: Ιανουάριος 1921. Map is an exact coverage and precise copy from  sheet Izmid from set:  Asia Minor 1:250,000. Series G.S.G.S. no. 2097. Published by Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. The title and place names are transliterated into English. This map represent a publication  issued by the  [Greek Royalist].
